Dobrii den!

Moi znakomie molodaia semia s rebenkom, poprosili zapostit dannoe obiavlenie.

Oni ishut moloduiy i energichnuiu devushku 23-29 let dlia babysitting s ih malenkoi dochkoi v Tel Avive. Na dannii moment pomosh neobhodima na tri polnih raza v nedelu.

Uslovia raboti, kotorie po-moemu ochen horoshie, mozno uznat u muza Dilradja po telefonu 050-8716724

Bil rad pomosh,
Jenia

Dobrii den:)

Mi  opat nahodimsia v prozesse bistrogo rosta i v dannoi situazii budem radi rassmotret resume software engineers so sleduiushimi dannimi:

Senior developer
B.Sc. in Computer Science/Software Engineering. 
Knowledge in : PERL / SQL / JAVASCRIPT programming. 
Must have at least 3 years experience in code developing. 
Proven Networking Architectures knowledge, under Unix operating systems. 

Junior developer
B.Sc. in Computer Science/Software Engineering. 
Knowledge in : PERL / SQL / JAVASCRIPT programming - advantage. 
1-2 years experience in code developing. 
Networking Architectures. 
Unix operating systems. 

System (IT) Analyst
B.Sc. in Computer Science/Information Systems Engineering. 
3 years experience in Information Systems analysis. 
Financial Systems analysis - advantage. 
Proven experience in writing Functional Specification Document. 

Bolee podrobnuu informaziu mozno naiti neposredstevnno na nashem site:

http://abc.shitrit.com/site/?page_id=22
